    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/5e4b11d5e948ceda04f1d2d3200fbfa5.poster.avif?t=1771788783\" width=1170 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/5e4b11d5e948ceda04f1d2d3200fbfa5.webm?t=1771788783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/5e4b11d5e948ceda04f1d2d3200fbfa5.mp4?t=1771788783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Project Pixel is an online level-editor game where you can build, play and share stages.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Pixel, a cute white square with simple platforming controls and a handy dash ability. Jump and dash through levels you make, others make, and that we have made in the story mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/d22c51660808573ae3ac57944d518514.poster.avif?t=1771788783\" width=1170 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/d22c51660808573ae3ac57944d518514.webm?t=1771788783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/d22c51660808573ae3ac57944d518514.mp4?t=1771788783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let your creativity run wild within the editor. Create easy, hard or just-perfect levels by yourself or with friends!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The editor is built with high ease-of-use and hands you control over pretty much everything, allowing you to tweak object properties, use hidden special triggers, customize level settings and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/a3eab07c2530417510115e1b8df981f4.poster.avif?t=1771788783\" width=1170 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/a3eab07c2530417510115e1b8df981f4.webm?t=1771788783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/a3eab07c2530417510115e1b8df981f4.mp4?t=1771788783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play an endless* stream of user-created levels in the Community Hub. Browse and explore others' creations!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Community Hub is a cozy little home for all levels alike. Published levels come here for everybody to play, with proper maintenance done by the game's characters**.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(* not quite endless)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(** sorry for not paying you, Meadow)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And pssst...! There's also a website version of the Community Hub so you can see it on other devices!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check it out under the links section of this store page.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/c2c6ba72f39af97b05c8cee84bd8f5e7.poster.avif?t=1771788783\" width=1170 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/c2c6ba72f39af97b05c8cee84bd8f5e7.webm?t=1771788783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337650/extras/c2c6ba72f39af97b05c8cee84bd8f5e7.mp4?t=1771788783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And it doesn't end here! Enjoy multiple customization options, a full-fledged story mode. And more, more, MORE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I can't fit everything I've spent the last year working on here, so I won't! Project Pixel has all the above and a little more, but I'll leave figuring out what that &quot;little more&quot; is up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I deeply hope you enjoy your experience if you decide to try the game. Farewell!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- DDMPlayer</p>",
